spamming our official social media pages with an address asking for
cryptocurrencies. Once again, we want to inform everyone that the CoolWallet
team will NEVER ask you for funds. Stay safe out there, and if you have received
messages that seem suspicious to you, feel free to direct message us for
clarification first before doing anything. We value each and everyone of you,
and we hope to continue providing top quality service to our community. 

 Thank you.

“Cryptocurrency markets are extremely fast-moving, but oftentimes,
cryptocurrency traders need to compromise security for their ability to react to
the markets. Users of #BUSD, #BNB, and Binance DEX who may want to trade
cryptocurrencies on their phones may do so and still safely store their virtual
assets almost immediately without having to wait until they are in front of a
computer. The CoolBitX team is very excited to be able to collaborate with 
Binance and provide a new support channel to their users." - CoolBitX CEO
Michael Ou x CryptonewsZ
